    "body": {
      "input": "Content: Example\n./restart.sh\ndatabase-snapshot.sh\nTake a local snapshot of the database, Pega webapps, and Pega app contexts) and save it in the /var/lib/pega/backup directory.\n\nParameters\n--snapshot-description <text> - Text description to identify the snapshot.\nExample\n./database-snapshot.sh --snapshot-description \"Test123\"\nframework.sh\nPerform an update or install of a GA version of any Pega Strategic applications offered in Pega Labs. Please see your Self-Service portal for a list of the available strategic apps.\n\nParameters\n--Action [install/update]\nDesired action to perform. install or update a strategic App\n\n--AppName [application name]\nApplication Name in Pega Labs required format (CRM, PegaMKT, PegaFFS, etc). Check the Strategic Apps dropdown list on your Self-Service Portal for a current list of available Applications"
    }
